                     ArcSoft Commander Agent Version 1.0.0
                            Release Notes

============================================================
CONTENTS:
============================================================
* Dependency
* Feature List
* Viewing the Change Log

============================================================
Dependency:
============================================================
This software is designed to run on Java SE 7 and later.

============================================================
Feature List:
============================================================
Support switch role.
Support input/output network monitor.
Support task transcoding.
Support mount remote storage.
Support startup and shutdown agent by command line.
Support agent configuration.
Support date time and time zone settings.
Support reboot / shutdown server.
Support DNS settings.
Support firewall settings.
Support route settings.
Support network settings.
Support cluster discovery protocol.

============================================================
Viewing the Change Log:
============================================================
See CHANGELOG in this directory.
